# Twitter Sentiment Analysis

This repository contains a Streamlit app for performing Twitter Sentiment Analysis. The app analyzes tweets and provides insights into sentiment trends, word clouds, hashtag frequencies, and a pie chart depicting the distribution of sentiments (positive, negative, and neutral).

